34
00:02:16.745 --> 00:02:21.305
to grow each year in volume of claims and in cost to support

35
00:02:21.305 --> 00:02:22.905
and rehabilitate injured people.

36
00:02:24.185 --> 00:02:28.805
In 2025, A CC received more than 2 million claims,

37
00:02:29.315 --> 00:02:31.845
71,000 more than the year before.

38
00:02:32.785 --> 00:02:35.045
We accepted 99% of these claims.

39
00:02:36.025 --> 00:02:40.125
Of the new claims, 55% were accepted within a minute,

40
00:02:40.585 --> 00:02:43.685
and 80% were accepted within 24 hours.

41
00:02:45.565 --> 00:02:48.655
More complicated claims such as treatment injuries,

42
00:02:49.575 --> 00:02:52.855
sensitive claims, and work-related Mental injuries take

43
00:02:52.855 --> 00:02:53.855
longer to assess,

44
00:02:54.515 --> 00:02:57.255
and on average, it took 57 days

45
00:02:57.395 --> 00:03:00.245
to assure a cover decision on these cohort,

46
00:03:02.135 --> 00:03:05.715
we spent over 8.1 billion in medical treatment,

47
00:03:05.815 --> 00:03:07.675
rehabilitation support,

48
00:03:08.015 --> 00:03:10.475
and weekly compensation, an increase

49
00:03:10.475 --> 00:03:12.435
