54
00:03:24.415 --> 00:03:25.865
This was primarily due

55
00:03:25.865 --> 00:03:28.745
to the reduction in the outstanding claims liability,

56
00:03:29.235 --> 00:03:32.065
which is the future cost of known claims.

57
00:03:33.965 --> 00:03:38.005
A CC managers one of New Zealand's biggest investment funds

58
00:03:38.185 --> 00:03:39.525
of 54 billion,

59
00:03:40.705 --> 00:03:44.245
and the investment team performed very well with returns

60
00:03:44.815 --> 00:03:45.925
